
@startuml

' Define Classes
class Aircraft {
  - name: String
  - type: String
  - yearOfManufacture: int
  - nextInspectionDate: Date
}

class PassengerAircraft {
  - numberOfSeats: int
}

class SeatCategory {
  - designation: String
  - hasEntertainment: boolean
  - numberOfSeats: int
}

class Flight {
  - flightNumber: String
  - date: Date
}

class Ticket {
  - ticketNumber: String
  - price: double
  - upgradeDesired: boolean
}

class Passenger {
  - name: String
  - passportNumber: String
}

class Airline {
  - name: String
}

class FlightAttendant {
  - name: String
  - employmentDate: Date
  - isChiefSteward: boolean
}

class Pilot {
  - name: String
  - employmentDate: Date
  - license: String
}

class Airport {
  - name: String
  - address: String
  - numberOfRunways: int
}

' Inheritance
PassengerAircraft <|-- Aircraft

' Associations
Aircraft "1" *-- "many" Flight : performs
Flight "1" *-- "many" Ticket : has
Ticket "1" o-- "1" SeatCategory : for
Flight "1" *-- "many" Passenger : has
Passenger "1" *-- "many" Ticket : has
PassengerAircraft "1" *-- "many" SeatCategory : has
Aircraft "1" o-- "0..1" Airline : belongs to
Airline "1" *-- "many" FlightAttendant : employs
Airline "1" *-- "many" Pilot : employs
Flight "1" *-- "many" FlightAttendant : has
Flight "1" "1" -- "1" Pilot : has captain
Flight "1" "0..2" -- "1" Pilot : has co-pilot
Flight "1" -- "1" Airport : departs from
Flight "1" -- "1" Airport : arrives at
Aircraft "1" -- "1" Airport : home airport (optional)

@enduml

---

### Notes:
- **Inheritance**: `PassengerAircraft` inherits from `Aircraft`.
- **Associations**:
  - Each `Aircraft` can perform multiple `Flight`s.
  - Each `Flight` can have many `Passenger`s and `Ticket`s.
  - Each `Ticket` is associated with one `SeatCategory`.
  - An `Airline` employs `Pilot`s and `FlightAttendant`s.
  - A `Flight` has one `Captain` (Pilot) and 0–2 `Co-Pilots` (Pilots).
  - A `Flight` has a `Departure Airport` and a `Destination Airport`.
  - An `Aircraft` may have a `Home Airport`.

